item.description: AutoML libraries automate the process of machine learning. PyCaret is an open source Python library for AutoML. In this article, I explore this library using the Pima Indian Diabetes dataset with a detailed tutorial. This article has been published as a part of Blogathon on Analytics Vidhya.
